A '' 'uwahimbye firime' '', na none '' 'uwahimbye umuziki wa firime' '', ni [[uwahimbye]], ku bufatanye bwa hafi na [[umuyobozi wa firime]] na / cyangwa [[producer wa firime | producer]], [[Umuziki wa Firime]] ya firime cyangwa televiziyo, cyane cyane mubice bya [[nyuma yumusaruro]]. Igihembo cya firime cyingenzi cyane ni [[Oscar | Igihembo cya Academy]] (Oscar) kuri [[Oscar / Umuziki wa Filime Nziza | Umuziki wa Filime Nziza]] ("Amanota Yumwimerere").

Inkomoko yuwahimbye firime iri mu ntangiriro ya [[amateka ya firime]], mugihe [[film icecekeye]] e yari iherekejwe na [[piyano]] kandi abahimbyi ba mbere ba firime bakoresheje umuziki byumwihariko nka piyano kuri piyano. cyangwa nk '[[amanota]] yanditse kuri orchestre. Nyuma yo kuza kwa [[firime y'amajwi]] ni bwo umuziki wa firime wafashwe amajwi muri studio.
